Can't you see they are busy?

194
00:12:29,780 --> 00:12:30,620
Busy?

195
00:12:31,070 --> 00:12:33,430
♪Time flows, yet pain stays above♪

196
00:12:33,430 --> 00:12:35,920
♪How much sorrow must one keep♪

197
