198
00:12:37,340 --> 00:12:38,180
Let's go, quickly.

199
00:12:39,180 --> 00:12:40,020
Come on.

200
00:12:45,100 --> 00:12:45,980
(So this is)

201
00:12:46,740 --> 00:12:48,940
