♪Dreams linger in memories untold♪

207
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:38,760
♪Our story written in fires of old♪

208
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:42,800
♪Your face in moonlight♪

209
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:46,040
♪So close, yet cold♪

210
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:51,640
♪Trapped in amber, love turned to stone♪

211
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:57,760
♪A ghost of you pierces my soul♪

212
00:13:58,080 --> 00:14:00,160
♪Chains of fate, but I won't let go♪

213
00:14:00,160 --> 00:14:04,440
♪Tears cling, refusing to fall♪

214
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:09,080
♪Through cycles of time♪

215
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:12,120
♪I'd still choose you above all♪

216
00:14:12,680 --> 00:14:15,680
♪So I'll shatter♪

217
00:14:16,160 --> 00:14:19,200
♪The mirrors of destiny's hand♪

218
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:24,920
♪Command the clouds, rewrite heaven's demand♪

219
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:31,560
♪Sword raised high♪

220
00:14:32,160 --> 00:14:35,280
♪Burn the threads of time♪

221
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:38,280
♪To tear through the stars♪

